5000|$|Subscriber edge router: Also {{called a}} Customer <b>Edge</b> <b>router,</b> {{is located at}} the edge of the subscriber's network, it also uses EBGP to its provider's Autonomous System. It is {{typically}} used in an (enterprise) organization.|$|E
